N2  - The article presents news briefs related to events involving the Academy of Management. Professor C.L. Jamison of the University of Michigan was elected Dean of the Fellows of the Academy. Academy President Harold Koontz has been elected a Fellow of the International Academy of Management. Donald A Woolf has been named associate professor of management at the University of Colorado.
